{"tid":158830,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"呢間學校痴線到走去ban《美女與野獸》","createTime":"2017-03-16T14:16:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-16T20:15:44.000Z","uid":3904,"like":2,"dislike":41,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c6fb87ba46a8849396100155e2f2c0248809237f","tid":158830,"uid":3904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T14:16:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2woM9q4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2woM9q4.jpg&h=ed22ca6f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n話就話全港唯一一間音樂中小學<br />\n<br />\n但丑聞一蘿蘿<br />\n<br />\n幾年前有單疑似已婚女小提琴導師搭上學生嘅傳聞<br />\n<br />\n又有單校長擅自打通幾間校工宿舍變豪宅<br />\n<br />\n基督教喎"},{"pid":"447aa60e9663efda4b4ba8ec9b28a1864e90f38a","tid":158830,"uid":24623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T14:23:02.000Z","msg":"on99"},{"pid":"0c26d7f56b4308f16a4259bbd0056f6d8c3b199d","tid":158830,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T14:25:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>神不喜悅同性戀<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"cfd75cac954ceb2b036c3fc19219fbb4f2cf42dc","tid":158830,"uid":60831,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T14:26:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>神不喜悅同性戀<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </strong></span></span></blockquote><br />\n但神父喜歡玩細路仔屎忽 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb6ee19125444de5772d0cc1c3efa611853f2cbe","tid":158830,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T14:29:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c89c74aa98ebe21824c5f2809728387c874b1ab6","tid":158830,"uid":19501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T14:31:59.000Z","msg":"已婚女小提琴導師圖?"},{"pid":"6357b88c0ea93e50fd2c9a5f165385dc225cbcad","tid":158830,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T14:32:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>神不喜悅同性戀<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </strong></span></span></blockquote><br />\n但神父喜歡玩細路仔屎忽 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n天主教太衰<br />\n所以反猶既馬丁路德先要進行宗教改革"},{"pid":"764aecd8e2486a0c03f97482d094d9ee0612a5ac","tid":158830,"uid":3904,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T14:36:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>已婚女小提琴導師圖?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n肥鬼婆黎<br />\n<br />\n不過都係傳<br />\n廢事搞到連仔收律師信唔貼圖啦<br />\n<br />\n反正古典音樂圈都傳通天"},{"pid":"aa54bebde1c5c3e89f641181907151935291b0c9","tid":158830,"uid":82829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T14:39:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>已婚女小提琴導師圖?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n肥鬼婆黎<br />\n<br />\n不過都係傳<br />\n廢事搞到連仔收律師信唔貼圖啦<br />\n<br />\n反正古典音樂圈都傳通天</blockquote><br />\n個學生受咗咩刺激<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a80bdb9ceead23d67ef87a812b3d8ae8a0f652d1","tid":158830,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T14:42:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-_JjepOk151o/U5CtxNPmz0I/AAAAAAAABK8/KvB7E_9fE08/s1600/%E4%BB%A4%E4%BA%BA%E6%88%B0%E6%85%84%E7%9A%84%E6%A0%BC%E6%9E%97%E7%AB%A5%E8%A9%B1_new.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F4.bp.blogspot.com%2F-_JjepOk151o%2FU5CtxNPmz0I%2FAAAAAAAABK8%2FKvB7E_9fE08%2Fs1600%2F%25E4%25BB%25A4%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%2588%25B0%25E6%2585%2584%25E7%259A%2584%25E6%25A0%25BC%25E6%259E%2597%25E7%25AB%25A5%25E8%25A9%25B1_new.jpg&h=9ee5bd47&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.23yy.com/upload/2015/03/19/3c22546f-d952-4312-8af6-e8230cd15bf1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.23yy.com%2Fupload%2F2015%2F03%2F19%2F3c22546f-d952-4312-8af6-e8230cd15bf1.jpg&h=3417c2ab&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"84723861f85795944678556a67c046fbe6d87fb8","tid":158830,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T14:44:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">回到現實：10個迪士尼童話的黑暗原型</span><br />\n<br />\n迪士尼童話故事之所以美好，就是因為那都經過改編再改編，事實上與童話故事原型相同的部分，大概只剩下他們一樣是「王子」跟「公主」了。像是白雪公主和老爸大搞不倫、裡頭的王子其實是戀屍癖...如果這種程度的「真實」你還能接受，那就接著看其他童話的「原型」吧。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">1. 小美人魚</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/583/d583373.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F583%2Fd583373.jpg&h=e69d0b91&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n迪士尼裡，王子最終跟小美人魚在一起，但事實上，王子愛上了其他女孩，逼的人魚公主必須取捨：到底該殺死王子、用他的鮮血恢復成人魚身份，還是就這樣變成海裡的泡泡，最終人魚公主選擇了自我犧牲。而相信我，這已經是最不殘忍的故事。"},{"pid":"3f4c9e7ff29c1e7a73159d0f7cd8e9d06311d388","tid":158830,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T14:45:33.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">2. 灰姑娘</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/583/d583381.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F583%2Fd583381.jpg&h=7b01c33d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n灰姑娘的小腳丫的確是註冊商標，但這也苦了想穿上玻璃鞋的她的兩個姐姐，因為她們腳太大了，為了塞進去，她們一個切掉腳趾、一個切掉腳跟，但這樣怎麼可能蒙混過關嘛！灰姑娘如願穿上自己的玻璃鞋，並且使役小鳥啄瞎姊姊們的雙眼，並用木箱蓋壓斷後母的脖子，成功報仇......這告訴我們，千萬別去惹女人。"},{"pid":"3153f0dee7e0f9a6aad9d4c2787864f1d188d737","tid":158830,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T14:46:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>3.獅子王</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/583/d583380.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F583%2Fd583380.jpg&h=b7abc3a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不覺得獅子王跟手塚治蟲的《森林大帝》(小白獅王)很像嗎？但迪士尼堅稱這是發想自莎士比亞的《哈姆雷特》，那個最後全部人死光光的大悲劇。做為辛巴原型的哈姆雷特王子雖然報仇成功，但也失去了愛人，最後還死在塗有劇毒的長劍下...Hakuna Matata～"},{"pid":"e3aa52ff6071ff99ce0c5527edb261eb2e3c70da","tid":158830,"uid":550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T14:47:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 以前做書店見識過呢間學校啲家長<br />\n除咗西女人諗唔到用咩形容詞形容佢地<br />\n痴痴呆呆坐埋一枱"},{"pid":"04be83635f42918e6ccf0b45f4863c84f64cfed7","tid":158830,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T14:47:39.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">4.阿拉丁</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/583/d583383.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F583%2Fd583383.jpg&h=3924c440&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n看也知道是天方夜譚裡的《阿里巴巴與四十大盜》，雖然這故事沒啥有趣，但電影版續作卻有點恐怖。阿里巴巴的哥哥─戈西姆，是阿拉丁中阿拉丁父親的原型，這個角色最後被殺死且分屍，屍塊被堆在藏有寶藏的洞穴中警告探險者。最後阿里巴巴請裁縫將戈西姆的屍體逢在一起，讓親友以為是死於疾病。"},{"pid":"eae4614e2e010225a8fdd324b408e53a4b07998f","tid":158830,"uid":6213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T14:47:49.000Z","msg":"睇完套戲 根本唔覺得有咩同性戀情節<br />\n廠商拎黎炒作 d宗教學校衝曬出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35b322cfa8b6f2be489eb5136b0447bee9a615cc","tid":158830,"uid":34628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T14:48:14.000Z","msg":"神父又係你<br />\n鬼父又係你"},{"pid":"652454436ac40cc03ca8fb550f679de1a754687f","tid":158830,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T14:48:46.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">5.睡美人</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/583/d583382.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F583%2Fd583382.jpg&h=f58ec4de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一個吻或許真的能喚醒公主，但可惜在1634年的原著中，王子根本沒有要喚醒公主的意思。美人公主在前，而且怎麼叫都不會醒，於是王子迷姦了她，然後拍拍屁股走人，睡美人則邊睡邊懷孕邊生下雙胞胎，還是其中一個孩子吸吮她的手指，把針的碎片吸出來才把他老媽叫醒...這不是撿屍，什麼才是撿屍？"},{"pid":"f51e1f74cc190cd85f9e9c37a8c213b108e6e3d1","tid":158830,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T14:49:40.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">6.大力士</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/583/d583376.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F583%2Fd583376.jpg&h=ae7d05f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n首先，大力士海格力斯的媽媽並不是天后赫拉，而是宙斯誘姦了別人的老婆、底比斯國王安菲特律翁之妻阿爾克墨涅，所以才會半人半神。小時候的海格力斯，用里拉琴誤殺自己的音樂老師利諾斯，和公主墨伽拉結婚生子，卻因為赫拉的詛咒發瘋，誤殺自己的小孩，為了消除罪孽才有了之後的12偉業，反正他結了三次婚，還有超多同性愛人。"},{"pid":"8097d5a6b04d1b3c0339979f6cf7aad496cf7ee1","tid":158830,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T14:50:30.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">7.狐狸與獵犬</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/583/d583377.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F583%2Fd583377.jpg&h=62d7056b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n這個被票選為迪士尼中最感人的故事，改編自1967年著的知名小說，內容同樣會讓你淚崩。小說中的狐狸陶德為了躲避獵犬小銅主人的追殺，筋疲力竭而死，而小銅的主人因為想養老而決定搬家，只是他臨走前，用獵槍斃了小銅，超渣的。"},{"pid":"6b8fae5095b0e9aadbc8f6afa8fe6c2ab3890fff","tid":158830,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T14:51:09.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">8.鐘樓怪人</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/583/d583379.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F583%2Fd583379.jpg&h=775d1759&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在雨果的原著小說中，主教福羅諾跟怪人加西莫多都愛著愛絲梅拉達，但她卻愛著隊長菲比斯，菲比斯玩弄了愛絲梅拉達並誣罪於她。可憐的街頭表演者淪為人人喊打的階下囚，還數度差點被福羅諾強暴，最後愛絲梅拉達被福羅諾陷害而處以絞刑，加西莫多在憤怒之下，高舉福羅諾從聖母院高處摔下。看著愛絲梅拉達和福羅諾的屍骨，加西莫多發出悲鳴，從此消失無蹤。"},{"pid":"457a142fc92f25705966139b6a40bd3d1f9692a7","tid":158830,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T14:52:36.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">咩叫斷背情節? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n寫通告炒咗佢啦</span></span><br />\n<br />\n係都寫同性戀情節"},{"pid":"d4f087cff19a0e0de72cf425e493f6ff1a37a10b","tid":158830,"uid":649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T14:52:36.000Z","msg":"仲要一定要人回"},{"pid":"8ad12ad00a4692b7543920afb77d8df1ebdbe66c","tid":158830,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T14:52:43.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">9.小飛俠</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/583/d583378.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F583%2Fd583378.jpg&h=bbf717c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n據「彼得潘」作者詹姆斯&middot;馬修&middot;貝瑞博物館的比爾表示，貝瑞在原版小說中，將彼得潘營造成一個殺人鬼，他曾描寫：「當孩子們長大了，那就違反了永無島的規則，彼得會以最為惡毒的報復心態，快速的殺了那些長大的孩子們。」也有一說是，彼得潘會把不想長大的孩子帶到永無島，在裡面永遠不會長大，但當小孩子表達出想長大時，就會被小飛俠殺掉。"},{"pid":"f6bbe50d3c9c4778da6a721725a4661077390350","tid":158830,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T14:54:07.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">10.風中奇緣</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/583/d583372.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F583%2Fd583372.jpg&h=2a370b0f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n寶嘉康蒂是真實存在的歷史人物，而約翰史密斯則從印地安人手中綁架了她，她被英國視為人質，並在慫恿下加入基督教，從此受名麗貝卡&middot;羅爾夫，她出席英國社交圈，被英國人作為「成功開化」的宣傳工具，最後得了不知名的疾病而死。<br />\n<br />\n欸～其實喪女各人是頗喜歡暗黑童話的，之前一直要找限制級成人格林童話，但每個地方都售罄啊！！把這件事跟朋友抱怨，結果還被說是心理變態人格扭曲，法課由咧。<br />\n<br />\n其實以現在的年紀（呃，有點悲傷）來說，暗黑童話的內容更有警世寓意，而且也更震撼人心，畢竟人還是得從美麗幻想中長大啊是吧...？"},{"pid":"6ada08af2de9ba6b902cbda1d9dabb39ca4db62b","tid":158830,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T14:58:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-_JjepOk151o/U5CtxNPmz0I/AAAAAAAABK8/KvB7E_9fE08/s1600/%E4%BB%A4%E4%BA%BA%E6%88%B0%E6%85%84%E7%9A%84%E6%A0%BC%E6%9E%97%E7%AB%A5%E8%A9%B1_new.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F4.bp.blogspot.com%2F-_JjepOk151o%2FU5CtxNPmz0I%2FAAAAAAAABK8%2FKvB7E_9fE08%2Fs1600%2F%25E4%25BB%25A4%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%2588%25B0%25E6%2585%2584%25E7%259A%2584%25E6%25A0%25BC%25E6%259E%2597%25E7%25AB%25A5%25E8%25A9%25B1_new.jpg&h=9ee5bd47&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.23yy.com/upload/2015/03/19/3c22546f-d952-4312-8af6-e8230cd15bf1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.23yy.com%2Fupload%2F2015%2F03%2F19%2F3c22546f-d952-4312-8af6-e8230cd15bf1.jpg&h=3417c2ab&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.k165.com/images/movies/full/cbcc58b9d318aff3481be247c05b4880aaba2847.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.k165.com%2Fimages%2Fmovies%2Ffull%2Fcbcc58b9d318aff3481be247c05b4880aaba2847.jpg&h=445866d2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cd300b455ac9c74cc8b183530cffa43c556cdf05","tid":158830,"uid":30487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T14:58:37.000Z","msg":"耶撚=戇撚鳩"},{"pid":"6643a33d315573f0a663d7aef00081e661befb63","tid":158830,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T14:59:49.000Z","msg":"收皮啦耶撚好嗎"},{"pid":"3a75db07a2b6ccce047629a136a70932f4940185","tid":158830,"uid":22240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T15:16:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/16/231647_6cb23dfaf3091ca3719ac2d2281bcdb6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F16%2F231647_6cb23dfaf3091ca3719ac2d2281bcdb6.jpg&h=152f439b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e7a004123c979cc0ca6b1f2a27f195797a504721","tid":158830,"uid":4559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T15:17:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ae242b33f6eaea44d9bce5b0b49d4bd3914736ad","tid":158830,"uid":1833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T15:24:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">耶穌同猶大都親吻過喇</span></span><br />\n佢地又係gay啊？<br />\n戇鳩耶撚"},{"pid":"157ededd53eb07042fcef283fb7a4ec90fdc98e2","tid":158830,"uid":4144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T15:27:33.000Z","msg":"平時d學生都應該比佢地洗哂腦"},{"pid":"07c61cdd3fa6893ed526429eb68a862ca24f3323","tid":158830,"uid":47819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T15:30:35.000Z","msg":"出回條托咩<br />\n我係家長睬你都on9<br />\n浪費紙張"},{"pid":"113d1d836fb2818111e01be3df54bd8ea88636d8","tid":158830,"uid":25148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T16:17:05.000Z","msg":"啲耶撚接受唔到現實 幾百年黎都活係本叫聖經既小說世界"},{"pid":"4615fd7cf84224325d893d1b7e2389a0aadc9346","tid":158830,"uid":33719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T16:50:24.000Z","msg":"耶撚得啖笑"},{"pid":"30603f9838bc3dfbc286ae1f247d31c0e7eec1a8","tid":158830,"uid":1788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T17:03:42.000Z","msg":"係通告寫聖經係咩語境<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9c9f2b15d56543e78fd38d2a0f5a1f8b275e0b3","tid":158830,"uid":2959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T17:10:15.000Z","msg":"簽回條<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8daf2d36c6da8afe86016df3db2e24487c96eebf","tid":158830,"uid":3904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T17:11:00.000Z","msg":"先旨聲明，我係信神嘅<br />\n<br />\n但係極之睇唔過眼啲所謂教會嘅耶撚<br />\n<br />\n當初新教係因為睇唔過眼天主教廷嘅腐敗而另起一個新教（當然都同政治有關）<br />\n<br />\n但而家嘅新教教會，比之天主教更加腐敗，<br />\n<br />\n曲解聖經，奶共，搞小朋友，用神名義cap水<br />\n<br />\n上唔上天堂呢啲都係其次，呢啲耶撚直情係令我覺得蒙羞"},{"pid":"fe5b57ad46eeaf4d76b55116cd2e2c548931d017","tid":158830,"uid":14021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T18:24:31.000Z","msg":"今日去左睇，所謂既同性戀情節都好隱晦下喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f9a0d6af44c702e363e9c0e7e06f963f576b327","tid":158830,"uid":14021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T18:25:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>今日去左睇，所謂既同性戀情節都好隱晦下喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n隱晦到好似冇咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"140a6b1cbcb2aeaa313960a25602c673f572cad4","tid":158830,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T18:33:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/16/231647_6cb23dfaf3091ca3719ac2d2281bcdb6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F16%2F231647_6cb23dfaf3091ca3719ac2d2281bcdb6.jpg&h=152f439b&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11d52044d0a75111733970634a311aa87ae0f8ec","tid":158830,"uid":21526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T18:35:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇完套戲 根本唔覺得有咩同性戀情節<br />\n廠商拎黎炒作 d宗教學校衝曬出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n同感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fad06d1fb84292d47e7ae9cfad806ec00f3bd9e","tid":158830,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T18:36:01.000Z","msg":"原因係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">神</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"158b54402b6f3ac711f11f8e06b38400d3978cb3","tid":158830,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T18:57:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8f59c7419c7d99fa9e8555ada55ba839b0eb1c7","tid":158830,"uid":70063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T19:03:25.000Z","msg":"最憎偽善撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d8f36ccd37447c468a451d4eee78f3050a6e4ee","tid":158830,"uid":16185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T19:15:11.000Z","msg":"根據佢地聖經，人都係神整出黎，咁點解要整完同性戀又ban？"},{"pid":"57b9d1bf3f5add725b37e747746f5b388d6d8504","tid":158830,"uid":47210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T19:22:04.000Z","msg":"一邊嗌神愛世人, 逼人信教<br />\n一邊周圍唱神不喜悅呢樣嗰樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n嗰堆神不喜悅嘅咪又係神製造出嚟, 話要愛嘅世人<br />\n咁同話神大細超, 講一套做一套有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"755cb8cc5ba21e8fd645ccfd83e6be3d8c08647b","tid":158830,"uid":47210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T19:22:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>根據佢地聖經，人都係神整出黎，咁點解要整完同性戀又ban？</blockquote><br />\n因為神不喜悅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bf07eed336acb00b97e3059eca7ea474b0b8385","tid":158830,"uid":5724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T19:35:23.000Z","msg":"好彩無讀呢間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n細個呀媽差啲中伏隊我入去讀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd671cc55fed53481d71e62554d638bdb2ff0c2a","tid":158830,"uid":5724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T19:39:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">耶穌同猶大都親吻過喇</span></span><br />\n佢地又係gay啊？<br />\n戇鳩耶撚</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/W62054h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW62054h.jpg&h=9e95675c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}